text: Åsa Magnusson (born 26 September 1964) is a Swedish freestyle skier. She won a silver medal in ski ballet at the FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships 1997. She also competed at the 1989, 1991 and 1995 world championships. == References == == External links == * Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female freestyle skiers
